OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FIran has launched fresh attacks on US
OL,7,Fallies in the Gulf, in response to
OL,8,Fearlier airstrikes by the United
OL,9,FStates military.
OL,11,FThe US launched strikes on Iranian
OL,12,Fmilitary sites on Tuesday night, after
OL,13,Fblaming Tehran for the crash of an
OL,14,FAmerican Apache attack helicopter.
OL,16,FThe escalation further strains a
OL,17,Ffragile ceasefire and complicates
OL,18,Fnegotiations aimed at permanently
OL,19,Fending the war that began in February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
