OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FIran's top diplomat vowed overnight
OL,7,Fthat there would be a response to the
OL,8,Fnew US strikes.
OL,10,FIranian forces "will leave no attack
OL,11,For threat unanswered," Iranian Foreign
OL,12,FMinister Abbas Araghchi said in a post
OL,13,Fon X.
OL,15,F"Leave our region if you want to be
OL,16,Fsafe."
OL,26,@rD@POUsD@VO]wD@AOUxD@FO]
