OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FJordan said on Wednesday it shot down
OL,7,Ffive incoming missiles launched by
OL,8,FIran, which Iran said targeted the
OL,9,FMuwaffaq Salti Air Base, which has
OL,10,Fhosted American F-35 fighter jets and
OL,11,Fother aircraft.
OL,13,FJordan's state-run Petra news agency
OL,14,Fcarried the statement from its
OL,15,Fmilitary, which added that there were
OL,16,Fno injuries in the attack and that
OL,17,Fexplosives experts had examined the
OL,18,Fdebris from the interceptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
