PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FIran launched attacks on sites in
OL,7,FBahrain, Kuwait, which both sounded
OL,8,Falerts and fired air defenses in
OL,9,Fresponse.
OL,11,FThe latest strikes come after
OL,12,FWashington blamed Tehran for the
OL,13,Fcrashing of an American attack
OL,14,Fhelicopter, which officials say
OL,15,Fcollided with an Iranian drone on
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,18,FIt wasn't clear whether the collision
OL,19,Fwas intentional, and the crash is
OL,20,Fcurrently under investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
