OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FThe Apache attack helicopter went down
OL,7,Foff the coast of Oman, while
OL,8,Fpatrolling the Strait of Hormuz - a
OL,9,Fcrucial shipping channel that Iran has
OL,10,Fhad a hold over since Israel and the
OL,11,FUS launched the conflict on February
OL,12,F28.
OL,14,FIts two crew members were rescued by a
OL,15,FUS sea drone ` the first incident of
OL,16,Fits kind in American military history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
