PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump said the
OL,7,Fcrew members were "safe and uninjured"
OL,8,Fbut added: "Nevertheless, the United
OL,9,FStates must, of necessity, respond to
OL,10,Fthis attack."
OL,12,FWith the already delicate ceasefire
OL,13,Fstrained even further, fighter jets
OL,14,Ffrom the US Air Force and Navy carried
OL,15,Fout out strikes on "air defense,
OL,16,Fground control stations, and
OL,17,Fsurveillance radar sites" in Iran on
OL,18,FTuesday ` prompting retaliation by
OL,19,FIran.
OL,26,@yD@YO]
