OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FIran acknowledged strikes around
OL,7,FBandar Abbas and Qeshm Island, but
OL,8,Fgave no details on the damage.
OL,10,F"The operation was a proportional
OL,11,Fresponse to recent attacks on US
OL,12,Fforces and international commercial
OL,13,Fships transiting regional waters," US
OL,14,FCentral Command said.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@bO]
