OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FOfficials from both sides have
OL,7,Fstruggled to reach a deal to
OL,8,Fpermanently end the conflict after a
OL,9,Fceasefire was agreed upon in April,
OL,10,Fparticularly as Israel intensifies and
OL,11,Fexpands its military campaign in
OL,12,FLebanon against Iranian-backed
OL,13,Fmilitary group Hezbollah.
OL,15,FIran and Israel exchanged fire on
OL,16,FSunday for the first time since the
OL,17,Ffragile truce took effect, partly
OL,18,Ftriggered by Israeli strikes on
OL,19,FLebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
