PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FOn Tuesday Iranian state television
OL,7,Fsaid that Israeli attacks had killed
OL,8,Fat least two members of the country's
OL,9,Fair-defence units.
OL,11,FBoth sides announed on Monday
OL,12,Fafternoon that they would halt attacks
OL,13,Fafter pleas for calm by President
OL,14,FTrump, but the ceasefire remained as
OL,15,Fdelicate as ever.
OL,17,FDespite the latest flaring of
OL,18,Fconflict, Trump said earlier this week
OL,19,Fthat he is still optimistic over a
OL,20,Flonger-lasting peace deal being struck.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FMediators, led predominantly by
OL,7,FPakistan, have been trying for weeks
OL,8,Fto get a deal across the line.
OL,9,FHowever, both Iran and the US have
OL,10,Ftaken hardline positions.
OL,12,FWashington wants to see Iran give up
OL,13,Fits stockpile of highly enriched
OL,14,Furanium, which is believed to have
OL,15,Fbeen buried by American airstrikes
OL,16,Fduring the 12-day war in 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FHowever, Tehran is refusing that and
OL,7,Fdemanding relief from sanctions. It
OL,8,Falso wants the release of frozen
OL,9,Fassets even before a final agreement
OL,10,Fis in place, something rejected by
OL,11,FTrump.
OL,13,FIsrael's military said on Wednesday it
OL,14,Fhad launched multiple strikes in
OL,15,Fsouthern Lebanon over the past day,
OL,16,Ftargeting Hezbollah infrastructure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
