PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781125879
OL,3,CIran attacks Gulf after US launches
OL,4,Cairstrikes over downing of helicopter
OL,6,FThe continued fighting between Israel
OL,7,Fand Hezbollah is still a top Iranian
OL,8,Fpriority, while Lebanon's government
OL,9,Fhas been taking an increasingly hard
OL,10,Fline against Hezbollah but remains
OL,11,Funable to disarm the powerful militia.
